## Best Practices

### DO ✅

```html
<!-- Use Tailwind utilities -->
<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">

<!-- Organize classes logically -->
<div class="flex items-center w-full p-4 bg-white rounded-lg">

<!-- Use responsive prefixes -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-4 md:grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-1">

<!-- Extract repeated patterns to components -->
<button class="btn-primary">Save</button>
```

### DON'T ❌

```html
<!-- Don't use inline styles -->
<div style="background-color: white; padding: 24px;">

<!-- Don't create custom classes when Tailwind works -->
<div class="my-custom-container">  <!-- Use Tailwind instead -->

<!-- Don't use arbitrary values excessively -->
<div class="p-[23px]">  <!-- Use standard spacing scale -->

<!-- Don't ignore responsive design -->
<div class="w-96">  <!-- Should scale down on mobile -->
```

